TSL (nke bụbu Tobacco Sales Ltd)(ZSE: TSL) bụ ụlọ ọrụ dabere na Harare, Zimbabwe
TSL tọrọ ntọala na 1957 dị ka ụlọ ahịa na-ere ụtaba, na njedebe 1960s malitere ịgbasa n'ime ngwa agha na agronomy
Edepụtara ngwaahịa ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na Zimbabwe Stock Exchange na ndepụta ngwaahịa ya, Zimbabwe Industrial Index
